Himachal Pradesh is home to many untouched and lesser-known villages that offer breathtaking landscapes and a peaceful retreat. Malana is famous for its ancient traditions, Kalpa boasts stunning views of Kinnaur Kailash, Rakchham is a paradise for trekkers, Barot is perfect for nature lovers, and Tirthan Valley offers tranquil riverside escapes. Whether you seek adventure or relaxation, these hidden gems are worth exploring. Plan your journey with **Pahari Yatri** and experience the true essence of Himachal!
